Just a day after Father's Day, rapper Cassper Nyovest has announced he is going to be a dad. He shared the good news with his followers on his social media platforms. He said: ''I'm going to be a father Any Minute Now so I decided 2 name my album #AMN (Any Minute Now). The album cover is an actual scan of my son in his beautiful mother's womb. Excited about dis album but I'm more excited bout being a dad 2 a beautiful baby boy. #AMN drops September 11th.'' According to the grapevine, Cassper has been dating KwaZulu-Natal-born socialite Thobeka Majozi. She has been a great supporter of the motswako rapper in the last couple of years. She has even posted pictures of herself wearing Cassper Nyoyest's merchandise.  